com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.renderer
Interface HasLegend

Deprecated. This interface is the porting of equivalent functionality in the Rhizosphere javascript library that is scheduled for rewrite (http://code.google.com/p/rhizosphere/issues/detail?id=120). It is likely to change significantly. 

@Deprecated
public interface HasLegend

Interface for RhizosphereRenderer instances to declare whether a legend should be added to the visualization to explain renderings attributes.
